a field of flowers.

455
00:20:58.750 --> 00:21:00.250
Oh, that's it!

456
00:21:00.620 --> 00:21:02.250
That's the field of flowers!

457
00:21:02.710 --> 00:21:04.080
Of course!

458
00:21:04.081 --> 00:21:06.380
They're not flowers
on Rafiki's map.

459
00:21:06.580 --> 00:21:07.880
They're stars!

460
00:21:08.120 --> 00:21:12.000
